stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> draft
  draft --> intake_received: submit_intake
  intake_received --> preprocessing: validate_payload
  preprocessing --> compliance_analysis: ocr_and_normalize_complete
  preprocessing --> failed: ocr_failed
  compliance_analysis --> review_pending: obligations_and_risks_resolved
  compliance_analysis --> failed: compliance_engine_error
  review_pending --> changes_requested: reviewer_requests_changes
  review_pending --> escalated: reviewer_escalates
  review_pending --> approved: reviewer_approves
  changes_requested --> preprocessing: resubmitted
  escalated --> review_pending: reassigned
  approved --> exported: export_generated
  approved --> failed: export_failed
  exported --> archived: close_workflow
  failed --> review_pending: manual_recovery
  archived --> [*]

  note right of review_pending
    tenant-scoped review queue
    decision and evidence are audited
  end note

  note right of failed
    failures emit incident events
    operator console can retry/replay
  end note
